# CODEOWNERS — review distribution for a small team.
#
# DEMO NOTE: this repository is a solo demonstration. In real use, the team is
# 4 people (1 tech lead, 1 dev, 1 senior data scientist, 1 data scientist) and
# the two senior ICs (tech lead + senior DS) share review authority. Here,
# `@b0rgcube` stands in for the whole team — branch protection's
# "require approvals" rule is disabled in this demo because GitHub doesn't
# allow self-approval on a PR you authored.
#
# In a real repo: every PR auto-requests both seniors; either can approve.
# When one senior is the author, the other reviews — automatic, because
# GitHub doesn't request review from the PR author.

# Default — every file in the repo
*                                       @b0rgcube

# Specs and ADRs
/specs/                                 @b0rgcube
/docs/adr/                              @b0rgcube

# CI / GitHub configuration
/.github/workflows/                     @b0rgcube
/.github/CODEOWNERS                     @b0rgcube
